{"article_id":"KbQdlmhruTpjVphD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Despite President Obama ' s lofty rhetoric last week","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that he ' d reached a \" historic \" nuclear understanding with Iran ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the White House Monday tamped down expectations","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that a final deal is in sight ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the two sides are still far apart on key sticking points .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"While Iran has committed to unprecedented limits on its nuclear program ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Iranian leaders still are demanding","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that any relief from economic sanctions","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"- America ' s key concession to Tehran -","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"be immediate ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"while White House officials say","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"the U.S. and its allies only will accept a phased-in approach to the lifting of sanctions .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The dispute ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"which looks to present a major hurdle","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"to reaching a final agreement by the end of June ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"is just one of several unanswered questions","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"that have top U.S. lawmakers wondering","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"whether an acceptable deal with Iran truly is as close","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"as Mr. Obama has portrayed .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Over the past few days , the White House consistently has tried to turn attention toward positive aspects of the agreement , such as Iran agreeing to greatly reduce its number of operating centrifuges and permit highly intrusive inspections of its nuclear facilities .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Energy Secretary Ernest Moniz continued that approach Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"telling reporters","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the preliminary deal centers on \" hard-nosed requirements \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that will give the international community certainty","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that Iran isn ' t pursuing a nuclear weapon .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"But officials also conceded","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that a final deal is far from the finish line ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and admitted","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that the question","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"of exactly when sanctions on Tehran will be lifted","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"was not resolved during last week ' s marathon negotiations .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"\" The deal ' s not done , \"","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"White House press secretary Josh Earnest said .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"\" You can ' t start talking about relieving sanctions","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"until we have reached definitive agreements","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"about how we ' re going to shut down every pathway","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"they have to a nuclear weapon .","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"Which is to say ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"one has to come before the other . \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Mr . Earnest went on to say","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"the Iranians still maintain","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"all sanctions must be lifted","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"immediately after a deal is signed .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"The deadline for a final agreement is June 30 .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The U.S. and the rest of the P5+1","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"- Britain , Germany , France , Russia and China -","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"maintain","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that sanctions must be lifted slowly in a process","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that would take months , possibly even years ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"depending on Iran ' s level of cooperation .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Obama has authority","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"to suspend most sanctions temporarily ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"but would need congressional authority","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"to permanently undo them .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"While the White House has stressed","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that any sanctions could be \" snapped back \" into place","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"if Iran doesn ' t live up to its commitments ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"officials in Tehran say","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"the reverse also is true :","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The country could restart all aspects of its nuclear program","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"if the U.S. doesn ' t make good on the promise","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to lift sanctions .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"\" Whatever work we have on the nuclear program can be restored . ... Our knowledge is local ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"and no one can take that away from us , \"","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Iranian Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif said last week .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Around the world , there are fears about exactly what Iran will do","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"once sanctions are lifted .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"he believes","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Iran will use the financial benefits of sanctions relief","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"to fund a \" terror machine \"","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that already is wreaking havoc across the region .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"\" We can not forget","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that Iran is pursuing a full-spectrum campaign","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"to expand its sphere of influence in the greater Middle East .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"America and its allies will need to be vigilant in combating all of Iran ' s other belligerent actions","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"as it uses the funding","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that would be derived from sanctions relief","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"to support proxy forces","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"and advance its stockpile of missiles , \"","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell said in a statement Monday .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"Not only does the preliminary deal not solve the sanctions question ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"it also does not force Iran to stop threatening Israel ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"nor does it require Iran to even recognize Israel ' s existence .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"\" The notion","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"that we would condition Iran not getting nuclear weapons in a verifiable deal on Iran recognizing Israel","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"is really akin to saying","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that we won ' t sign a deal","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"unless the nature of the Iranian regime completely transforms , \"","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"the president said in an interview with NPR .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"\" And that is ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"I think ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"a fundamental misjudgment . \"","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Meanwhile , the Senate Committee on Foreign Relations is set to vote next week on a bill","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"that would require Congress to sign off on any Iran deal .","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"It would prohibit the president from lifting any sanctions for 60 days ,","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"giving the House and Senate sufficient time","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"to review the agreement .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"Mr. Obama has vowed to veto the bill ,","depth":4},{"id":100,"text":"though key senators say","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"they nearly have the needed 67 votes","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"to override a veto .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Analysts say","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"the issue of when sanctions are lifted , and what guarantees are put in place","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"to assure potential investors","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"they won ' t suddenly reappear ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"is of utmost importance","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"as the two sides try and reach a final , binding deal .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"\" This question about sanctions is crucial in terms of when they are relaxed ,","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"but the pledge","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"to relax them","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"must be pretty durable","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"in order to convince businesses and individuals to make that fairly momentous decision","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"to invest there , \"","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"said Christopher Preble , vice president for defense and foreign policy studies at the libertarian Cato Institute .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":231,"left":209,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":135,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":128,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":121,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":119,"right":120,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":117,"right":118,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":6,"right":126,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":124,"right":125,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":7,"right":123,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":130,"right":133,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":13,"right":129